PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Communications of Ken Danby, of Guelph, Ontario, as a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the National Gallery of Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective July 22, 1991, in the place of Michael P. Bell, whose term will expire.
